T*
(0071:     row = cur.fetchone\(\) ) Tj
T*
(0072:     if row is None: ) Tj
T*
(0073:         return None ) Tj
T*
(0074:     if cur.description is None: ) Tj
T*
(0075:         raise RuntimeError\("fetchone_dict chamado sem SELECT \(cur.description=None\)"\) ) Tj
